@
  You are controling the worm by using cursor keys and your mission is to   1/9
  try to eat as many pizzas as possible. (Player two keys are Z and C)

  Write PWORM ? to find out the game options / parameters.

  If the game halts on your machine, first disable sound system using parameter
  /N (I dont know how well does the Midas sound system work)

