version 2.1                                                                 4/9

   + Two worms could cross in beta, now fixed.
   + 386 instructions removed (now game runs on 286 without music.)
   + New patterns in music module.
   + New better startup piccy
   + New charters added to font, and now u can use them at highscore list
     too!
   + Cursor added in highscore screen. (I didnt see any reason to add this,
     but some one requested.)

@
version 2.0 public beta                                                     5/9

   + Two player mode added!
   + SIN and COS values in table -> less cpu load.
   + Possibility to clear two-player mode wins.
   + Module musics (Old beeper/SB/AdLib routines removed)
   + Joystick support (Does it really work?)
   + New PRESS ENTER FOR NEWGAME OR ESC TO EXIT procedure..
   + Once again improved graphics.
   + Few samples fixed. (Now burp really sounds great!)
   + Cheat keys changed. (Now you can have fun again while searching them!)
   + Now uses 386+ instructions for Music mixing and Screen restores.
   + Pizza cant be laid on worm two anymore.

@
version 1.2                                                                 6/9

   + Program doesn't halt anymore if YOU don't have SB.
   + New parameter system.
   + New (better?) worm start point.
   + Better Pizzas (More meat)
   + Improved / faster font unit by me...
   + Internal DOC viewer added.
   + Adlib instrument #0 is now fully reseted by game. (Before it, game sounded
     different after other games... Nice..)
   + Assembler part to reserve memory. (Old one was slow 16 bytes reserver,
     It might take up to 5 seconds to reserve memory. Now it happends with
     12 assembler commands. And uses about 0.0001 seconds time...)
   + Some of the samples are better (Made by Sini)
   + Greetings screen bars variable speed.
   + Ok Ok, cheats still included, but better hidden.
@
version 1.11 Final Beta                                                     7/9

   + NOW ULTRA MEGA GIGA C00L SB SOUNDS!!!
   + Memory pageing problem fixed, now all samples should fully work.
   + Bigger things, you can figure this one out by yourself!
   + Once again, now about 25% faster than in 1.11beta. (uh, thinking about
     pizza formulas is HARD work, I used about 20 hours to get this ultra
     fast pizza method.)
   + Those new graphic pictures that I didn't get in time to be used with
     1.11beta
   + In beta version, there was bug with pizza wiping and placing
     routine.
   + Now loads all gfx to memory. (Makes playing from disk faster)
@
Version 1.11beta                                                            8/9

   + New MUCH faster pizza routine. Over 13 times (1300%) faster!
   + Most of graphic functions direcly written in code. 45% faster fonts
     and worm drawing.
   + WORKING Adlib Sound System!
   + New pictures by friend. (Not included yet!)
   + Training mode
   + Clear highscores 4-10 with R parameter!
   + And many little things, that I have just noticed while browsing code.
   + Now you can't die in highscore screen. (That happened some times in old
     version)
@
Version 1.1                                                                 9/9
   + Adlib Sound System! Yeah, it's included but forced off (GREAT EH?)
     In next version (1.2) there will be DIGITAL SOUND!
   + Worm becomes longer instantly after eating a pizza.
   + New start picture.
   + Different highscores screen!
   + New game backround !
   + N0T C00L dudeZ rem0ved from greet1ng5 list!
   + CHEATS REMOVED!  (NO FAIR)
